Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,CONTESTED-LOG. CONUS to squad. Eight datasets. One COA.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.14,0:00:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Force Design 2030 — INDOPACOM contested. Two hundred MRE pallets,\NAlbany Georgia to the 31st MEU at Itbayat, in fourteen days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight feeds fused on screen — BTS rail, MSI ports, AIS lanes, three\Nthousand ASAM piracy records, AFCENT, GCSS-MC, LaDe last-mile, and a …
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Operator types one sentence. The agent fires six typed tools on a\NKamiwaza-deployed model.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,route_conus, check_port_capacity, forecast_pirate_risk,\Ncheck_supply_chain_disruption, compute_last_mile, compare_options — …
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Three Courses of Action ranked. Recommended COA pulses neon — full\Nroute over the dark Pacific theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:01:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Two hundred MRE pallets — twenty-one days of subsistence for the MEU.\NSeven-day reserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Same code. Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL — on-prem inference, IL5 IL6 ready,\None hundred percent data containment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,CONTESTED-LOG. Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not\Nmonths.
